  "1864950": {
    "name": "杯丝特魔球",
    "steam_appid": 1864950,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >关于此游戏</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这款<strong>回合制排球RPG</strong>中，指导杯丝特运动战队吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1864950/extras/096e9cb7e7036ca63df7e3d3f15989b2.poster.avif?t=1767944364\" width=640 height=276 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1864950/extras/096e9cb7e7036ca63df7e3d3f15989b2.webm?t=1767944364\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1864950/extras/096e9cb7e7036ca63df7e3d3f15989b2.mp4?t=1767944364\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >杯丝特能通过彼此的情谊激发团队力量。无论是成为<strong>死党、搭档、竞敌还是恋友</strong>，它们都会解锁独一无二的组合技，足以扭转战局！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1864950/extras/782e7642d3c2d6b85cb201f95207bc16.poster.avif?t=1767944364\" width=640 height=354 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1864950/extras/782e7642d3c2d6b85cb201f95207bc16.webm?t=1767944364\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1864950/extras/782e7642d3c2d6b85cb201f95207bc16.mp4?t=1767944364\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >自由探索开放的世界，遇见性格迥异的评级教练。每位教练都承载着独特的故事线，唯有战胜他们提升评级，才能获得参加<strong>王冠系列赛</strong>的资格。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1864950/extras/05bdf26d53f8d0bba167d2703743a9f4.poster.avif?t=1767944364\" width=638 height=302 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1864950/extras/05bdf26d53f8d0bba167d2703743a9f4.webm?t=1767944364\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1864950/extras/05bdf26d53f8d0bba167d2703743a9f4.mp4?t=1767944364\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >所有的首领位置从一开始就会在你的地图上标注，你可以<strong>自由选择挑战顺序</strong>。每击败一位对手，其他首领就会变得更强，因此你无论选择哪条路，都将迎来充满挑战的登顶之旅。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在迷你战术网格上展开策略性回合制对决。当你持球时，可进行多次传球，策划猛攻；对方持球时，则需预判其攻势，及时组织防守。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1864950/extras/05a871238ddad7b798df971ae63ef59e.poster.avif?t=1767944364\" width=500 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1864950/extras/05a871238ddad7b798df971ae63ef59e.webm?t=1767944364\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1864950/extras/05a871238ddad7b798df971ae63ef59e.mp4?t=1767944364\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每只杯丝特都拥有独特的特质、优势与弱点，通过多样化的协作方式，为每场对战注入丰富的策略深度。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >想要进入魔球联赛，可不只是打球这么简单！击败评级教练后可以与他们互动交友，通过培养友情体验额外故事。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随着故事推进，你将结识伙伴、对手、<strong>企业赞助方</strong>，甚至还会遇见一位怀揣野心的神秘运动之王……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1864950/extras/76232a2dcb2bff96e9b01356abf5e687.poster.avif?t=1767944364\" width=414 height=354 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1864950/extras/76232a2dcb2bff96e9b01356abf5e687.webm?t=1767944364\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1864950/extras/76232a2dcb2bff96e9b01356abf5e687.mp4?t=1767944364\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
